window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Book four of the hit LitRPG series, Defiance of the Fall, with over 20 million views on </b><b><i>Royal Road</i></b><b>. </b></p> <p>Jump into a story that merges LitRPG elements with eastern cultivation. Class systems, skill systems, endless choices for progression - it has everything fans of the genre love! Explore a vast universe full of mystery, adventure, danger, and even aliens; where even a random passer-by might hold the power of a god.</p> <p>Follow Zac, as he struggles to stake out a unique path to power, as a mortal in a world full of cultivators.</p>"; 
